        <Heading tagName="h3" size="base3" family="serif" id="research-overview"
          >Research overview</Heading
        >
        <p>
          Research interests: specifically, structure & function of marine
          mammals, especially feeding in toothed and baleen whales; biomechanics
          & materials science of biological tissues; 3D printing of biological
          structures or biological analogues; basic fluid dynamics and effects
          of flow on organisms; fossils & paleontology Potential topics for
          students: marine biology & oceanography; anatomy & physiology;
          anything related to evolution (human and otherwise); science &
          religion; philosophy of science; bioethics; environmental issues
        </p>
